      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GREAT CHAT (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 8 lengths at this track in a handy 29.41 beating Hurry Tuncurry. The form from his last run stacks up well. Can measure up again. HELLO CHILLI (2) has a strong record this track and trip with five wins and three placings from 14 starts. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (29.69) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. STARRY ETHICS (4) finished fifth last time at Wentworth Park but could not have been more impressive before that in her quick 22.21 win at this track over 388m. Smart winner two back and looks a key chance on that form. ASCEND FERN (7) will be hard to beat despite making his debut at this circuit.",
